msgid ""
"**Custom Weak Forms (Pythonic)** — supports user-defined bilinear / "
"linear forms directly in Python, without a separate DSL such as UFL. "
"**End-to-End Autograd** — gradients flow natively through the entire "
"pipeline; FEniCS supports this via the external ``dolfin-adjoint`` "
"package. **Maturity** — reflects project age, ecosystem size, and "
"production deployments."
msgstr ""

